data.description: Introducing this stunning 3-bedroom, 3.5-bathroom home located in the desirable Glenmary neighborhood. As you step through the front door, you'll be greeted by a grand staircase and an inviting open-concept layout on the first floor. The living room on the main level features a beautiful stone fireplace, creating a cozy ambiance. Natural light floods the space, creating a warm and inviting atmosphere. The kitchen is a chef's dream, offering ample cabinetry for storage and plenty of counter space for meal preparation. Upstairs, a loft area overlooks the foyer and living room, adding a touch of elegance to the home's design.The primary  suite is generously sized and features a  spacious vanity area, a jet tub, and a walk-in shower, providing a luxurious retreat. Downstairs, you'll find a versatile space perfect for relaxation or entertaining with family and friends. Additionally, there is an extra room that can be used as a gym or home office, offering flexibility to suit your needs. A convenient kitchenette setup downstairs adds convenience for entertaining or hosting guests. The property boasts a park-like setting both in the front and back yard, providing a serene and picturesque environment. Notably, the backyard has been newly fenced for added security. Situated on the fairway, this home offers beautiful views and a tranquil setting. Don't miss the opportunity to make this exceptional property your own. Contact us today to schedule a viewing and experience the charm and elegance of this Glenmary gem.
